---
description: CephasOps architecture code review
alwaysApply: false
---

Review the code for safety violations.

Check for:

• manual TenantScope.CurrentTenantId
• manual EnterPlatformBypass / ExitPlatformBypass
• missing TenantScopeExecutor usage
• tenant-owned writes without CompanyId
• weakened guards:
  - SiWorkflowGuard
  - FinancialIsolationGuard
  - EventStoreConsistencyGuard
  - TenantSafetyGuard

Also verify:

• TenantScopeExecutor usage is correct
• Tenant-owned operations cannot run under platform bypass
• Platform bypass is justified and documented
• Tests exist for tenant-sensitive logic
• Documentation updates are included if architecture changed

Return:

1. Safe
2. Needs changes
3. Violations
4. Recommended fixes
